in creating vm tab
check the qemu agent
scsi controller virtio scsi

in Hard disk tab
bus/Device = SCSI
SCSI controller VirtIo
Cache write back
if it's on ssd drive check the discard

other tabs choose as you want

download the latest virtio for your proxmox
add it as a new cd allong side your windows iso to the vm

start the vm

windows will not find hard drives

load driver / browse to the virt disk
its in the vioscsi choose your windows type
install the drive

then install the windows

when windows is installed go to device manager
install everything that is not recognised from virtio disk

install the guest-agent from the disk

it's done


